# The `.structurizr` folder is Structurizr's working folder, which contains automatically generated files which should not be committed.
/.structurizr/*

# Re-include the directoy which contains useful thumbnail images:
!/.structurizr/1/

# The `workspace.json` is automatically generated by structurizr.
# We do not need to commit it, unless we want to disable Automatic layout, and instead be able to drag and arrange diagrams manually.
# The choice has been made to not commit `workspace.json`, because Automatic layout has been fine so far, and because Automatic layout saves time and reduces complexity by not having to visually design diagrams.
# The `workspace.json` does not lend itslef to be committed, resolving merge conflicts would be problematic and challenging.
workspace.json
